Task 2

variable -- Can able to store the data/Value in the memory. eg: _ab, abc, k211.


data type -- To define the type of data/value Eg: int,float,string


data structure -- Its a method to store the data in a structured way so that it can be easily created, viewed, and managed. Eg: Array,Linked list,Trees.


operator -- Used to perform an operation (arithmetic & logical). Eg a+b, 


keyword -- Basic syntax/ Reserved words & it cannot be used as variable. eg: if,else,true,false,try,etc


function inbuilt function --  predefined function which is already persent in framework. It can be accessed by calling the function name. Eg: sort(),len(),


